<h2 id="auditors-on-audit">Auditors on Audit</h2>

<h3 id="add-an-auditor-to-an-audit">Add an auditor to an audit</h3>
<pre class="highlight http"><code><span class="nf">POST</span> <span class="nn">/api/v1/audits/:audit_id/auditors</span> <span class="k">HTTP</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="m">1.1</span>
</code></pre>
